            "id": "https://romivandaele.com/works/bow-dress-2025/",
            "url": "https://romivandaele.com/works/bow-dress-2025/",
            "title": "Bow Dress (2025)",
            "summary": "The Bow Dress is a study in refined minimalism, crafted for those&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div>\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\"  data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"3\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://romivandaele.com/media/posts/32/gallery/IMG_2642-2.jpeg\" data-size=\"3024x4032\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://romivandaele.com/media/posts/32/gallery/IMG_2642-2-thumbnail.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://romivandaele.com/media/posts/32/gallery/IMG_2646-2.jpeg\" data-size=\"3024x4032\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://romivandaele.com/media/posts/32/gallery/IMG_2646-2-thumbnail.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://romivandaele.com/media/posts/32/gallery/IMG_4949.jpeg\" data-size=\"2944x3926\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://romivandaele.com/media/posts/32/gallery/IMG_4949-thumbnail.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n<div>The Bow Dress is a study in refined minimalism, crafted for those who value form and function in equal measure. Its sleek black silhouette is designed to endure—both in style and wear—offering a versatile piece that transitions effortlessly across occasions. Wide straps provide comfort and support, while the subtle bow detail at the chest, secured with a single button, adds a quiet yet distinctive focal point. The ruched lower half introduces a soft texture, ensuring the design remains dynamic without excess.</div>",
