        },
        {
            "id": "https://romivandaele.com/works/freckle-skirt-2025/",
            "url": "https://romivandaele.com/works/freckle-skirt-2025/",
            "title": "Freckle Skirt (2025)",
            "summary": "A clean silhouette with a refined touch. The Freckle Skirt is designed&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\"  data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"3\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://romivandaele.com/media/posts/30/gallery/IMG_2616.jpeg\" data-size=\"2589x3313\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://romivandaele.com/media/posts/30/gallery/IMG_2616-thumbnail.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"983\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://romivandaele.com/media/posts/30/gallery/IMG_2630.jpeg\" data-size=\"3024x4032\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://romivandaele.com/media/posts/30/gallery/IMG_2630-thumbnail.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://romivandaele.com/media/posts/30/gallery/IMG_2632.jpeg\" data-size=\"3024x4032\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://romivandaele.com/media/posts/30/gallery/IMG_2632-thumbnail.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p>A clean silhouette with a refined touch. The <strong data-start=\"97\" data-end=\"114\">Freckle Skirt</strong> is designed for effortless movement, with golden flecks adding a subtle shimmer. Its minimal design makes it easy to style—dress it up or keep it casual. Functional. Elegant. Made to last.</p>",
