        {
            "id": "https://romivandaele.com/works/split-flare-skirt-2025/",
            "url": "https://romivandaele.com/works/split-flare-skirt-2025/",
            "title": "Split Flare Skirt (2025)",
            "summary": "A striking split flare skirt designed for movement, confidence, and versatility. Tailored&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\"  data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"3\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://romivandaele.com/media/posts/29/gallery/IMG_2597.jpeg\" data-size=\"3024x4032\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://romivandaele.com/media/posts/29/gallery/IMG_2597-thumbnail.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"119\" data-end=\"465\">A striking split flare skirt designed for movement, confidence, and versatility. Tailored with a sleek silhouette that flares beautifully from the knee down, this piece offers an elevated yet effortless look. The subtle front split adds both structure and flow, making it perfect for everyday wear or standout styling.</p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"467\" data-end=\"647\">Pair it with a structured blazer for a refined aesthetic or dress it down with a relaxed knit for a modern twist. Whatever your style, this skirt is designed to make a statement.</p>",
