        {
            "id": "https://romivandaele.com/works/the-rembrandt-2025/",
            "url": "https://romivandaele.com/works/the-rembrandt-2025/",
            "title": "The Rembrandt (2025)",
            "summary": "The Rembrandt is a versatile statement piece that can be worn as a&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\"  data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"3\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://romivandaele.com/media/posts/27/gallery/DSC_8222_websize.jpeg\" data-size=\"1067x1600\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://romivandaele.com/media/posts/27/gallery/DSC_8222_websize-thumbnail.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1152\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://romivandaele.com/media/posts/27/gallery/DSC_8243_websize.jpeg\" data-size=\"1067x1600\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://romivandaele.com/media/posts/27/gallery/DSC_8243_websize-thumbnail.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1152\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p data-start=\"123\" data-end=\"469\">The Rembrandt is a versatile statement piece that can be worn as a structured top or styled as a \"kraag\" (collar) over other garments. Featuring sculpted pleats and an off-the-shoulder design, it brings a refined yet bold touch to any outfit. An oversized button detail adds a distinctive accent, enhancing its architectural silhouette.</p>\n<p data-start=\"471\" data-end=\"559\">Whether worn alone or layered, this unique piece offers endless styling possibilities.</p>\n<p data-start=\"471\" data-end=\"559\"> </p>\n<div dir=\"auto\">Model: @phaedravergeylen</div>\n<div dir=\"auto\">Make-up: @glow_geel</div>\n<div dir=\"auto\">Fotograaf: @evelynemertens.shoots</div>\n<div dir=\"auto\">Styling: @valeriedestyliste</div>",
            "image": "https://romivandaele.com/media/posts/27/DSC_8243_websize.jpeg",
