            "date_published": "2025-03-18T15:29:51+01:00",
            "date_modified": "2025-03-18T15:29:51+01:00"
        },
        {
            "id": "https://romivandaele.com/works/reno-skirt/",
            "url": "https://romivandaele.com/works/reno-skirt/",
            "title": "Reno Skirt (2025)",
            "summary": "Elevate your wardrobe with this stunning black skirt, a one off signature&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\"  data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"3\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://romivandaele.com/media/posts/26/gallery/DSC_8432-3_websize.jpeg\" data-size=\"1067x1600\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://romivandaele.com/media/posts/26/gallery/DSC_8432-3_websize-thumbnail.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1152\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p data-start=\"103\" data-end=\"360\">Elevate your wardrobe with this stunning black skirt, a one off signature piece. Designed for elegance and versatility, the skirt features intricate gold embroidery in a floral pattern, adding a touch of opulence to its sleek silhouette.</p>\n<p data-start=\"362\" data-end=\"602\">Perfect for formal occasions or statement styling, this piece effortlessly pairs with fitted tops and heels, offering a refined yet bold aesthetic. </p>\n<p data-start=\"362\" data-end=\"602\">Part of the Reno duet, with <a href=\"https://romivandaele.com/works/reno-blazer-2025/\">blazer</a> and skirt.</p>\n<p data-start=\"362\" data-end=\"602\"> </p>\n<address>Model: @phaedravergeylen<br>Make-up: @glow_geel<br>Fotograaf: @evelynemertens.shoots<br>Styling: @valeriedestyliste</address>",
