        {
            "id": "https://romivandaele.com/works/eclipse-2025/",
            "url": "https://romivandaele.com/works/eclipse-2025/",
            "title": "Eclipse (2025)",
            "summary": "This exquisite piece, commissioned by André for his beloved wife, Cindy, is&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\"  data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"3\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://romivandaele.com/media/posts/25/gallery/IMG_5333.jpeg\" data-size=\"2986x3377\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://romivandaele.com/media/posts/25/gallery/IMG_5333-thumbnail.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"869\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://romivandaele.com/media/posts/25/gallery/IMG_5338.jpeg\" data-size=\"2407x3209\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://romivandaele.com/media/posts/25/gallery/IMG_5338-thumbnail.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://romivandaele.com/media/posts/25/gallery/IMG_5168.JPEG\" data-size=\"1536x2048\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://romivandaele.com/media/posts/25/gallery/IMG_5168-thumbnail.JPEG\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://romivandaele.com/media/posts/25/gallery/IMG_5172.JPEG\" data-size=\"1046x3006\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://romivandaele.com/media/posts/25/gallery/IMG_5172-thumbnail.JPEG\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"2207\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://romivandaele.com/media/posts/25/gallery/IMG_5169.JPEG\" data-size=\"1436x2188\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://romivandaele.com/media/posts/25/gallery/IMG_5169-thumbnail.JPEG\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1170\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"flex-shrink-0 flex flex-col relative items-end\">\n<div>\n<div class=\"pt-0\">\n<div class=\"gizmo-bot-avatar flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-full\">\n<div class=\"relative p-1 rounded-sm flex items-center justify-center bg-token-main-surface-primary text-token-text-primary h-8 w-8\"><span style=\"color: var(--text-primary-color); font-family: var(--editor-font-family); font-size: inherit; font-weight: var(--font-weight-normal);\">This exquisite piece, commissioned by André for his beloved wife, Cindy, is a celebration of elegance and artistic innovation. The double-layered dress exudes a sense of mystery and allure with its semi-transparent fabric, creating a mesmerizing moiré effect as the layers interact. The subtle interplay of light and texture lends the garment an almost hypnotic quality, captivating the eye and drawing one into its intricate design.</span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn\">\n<div class=\"flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3\">\n<div class=\"flex max-w-full flex-col flex-grow\">\n<div class=\"min-h-8 text-message flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-normal break-words text-start [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5\" dir=\"auto\" data-message-author-role=\"assistant\" data-message-id=\"6066b856-9c7f-4657-bbdc-2d7372d06e0a\" data-message-model-slug=\"gpt-4o\">\n<div class=\"flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]\">\n<div class=\"markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert dark\">\n<p>The shoulders are adorned with delicate ribbons of fine strings, cascading gracefully to add a soft yet dynamic movement to the overall silhouette. These strings serve as both a functional and aesthetic feature, framing the shoulders and complementing the dress's flowing form. The combination of modern design techniques and timeless sophistication makes this dress not only a striking visual statement but also a deeply personal gift, embodying André's admiration for Cindy.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p> </p>",
            "image": "https://romivandaele.com/media/posts/25/IMG_5333.jpeg",
